    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta check out this absolute gem! Honestly, it's like stepping back in time\u2014this beauty is in showroom condition and looks like it hasn't aged a day. I've babied it since day one, so you won't find a single scratch or a speck of dust. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh car feel. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is your ride! Let's get you behind the wheel!",
