    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3 in concours-level condition. The S54B32 power plant remains factory-spec, benefiting from a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and proactive rod bearing replacement. The chassis is rock-solid, featuring a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate common fatigue points. Power is delivered through the sought-after Getrag 6-speed manual to a variable M differential lock. Every bushing, seal, and mechanical component has been maintained to an exacting standard. This is a turnkey example for the discerning collector who demands mechanical purity and peak performance.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
