    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to be listing this total stunner. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one\u2014it\u2019s spotless inside and out, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019ve been looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and kept in pristine condition, this is the one for you. I\u2019m so sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to be over the moon with it. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 46500.0,
