    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The mechanical integrity is superlative, with documented rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. Power is delivered through a precise six-speed Getrag manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. This example remains in an impeccable state of preservation, retaining its original paint depth and a cabin devoid of typical wear on the Nappa leather bolsters or interior trim. A turn-key acquisition for the enthusiast seeking a mechanically flawless, high-revving masterpiece.",
